-clone the rewuested repository
git clone  git clone https://github.com/dmst-sweng/git-intro.git

-update my repository with the latest version
git pull

-update tasks file after adding my name next to a task
git commit -a -m

-push changes 
git push

-create new branch for ppeponis 
git branch ppeponis

-go to ppeponis branch
git checkout ppeponis

-add my changelog file to the repository
git add changelog_ppeponis

-apply commit to local repository 
git commit -a -m "fix -z not working"

-update remote repository
git push -u origin ppeponis

-update local repsotiry once again
git pull

-go to our branch
git checkout master

-merge our branch with master
git merge ppeponis